{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1232a2d01e","title":"第一部分 黄兆其是“四人帮”在我省培植的资产阶级帮派头目","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1837e88f3f","index":0,"year":1977,"month":7,"day":null,"articleId":"1232a2d01e"}],"tags":[{"id":"33b85cb7de","name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"id":"3459654dae","name":"限制资产阶级法权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"40ffd466ef","name":"武斗","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"5f6c7e74b5","name":"派性","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"88958321be","name":"云南文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa048f8141","name":"夺权","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"ad51b2eae3","name":"批林批孔","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"cf6066d2fa","name":"浙江文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866","name":"黄兆其的部分罪行材料（1977.7）","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"img","author":"朱、黄专案组","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/1.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/2.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/3.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/4.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/5.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae25-bd924efbe866/6.jpg,https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives1/main/c14adb69-9919-45b0-ae2